Review_title: Authentic journey from prision to freedom
Review_Text: Fantastic documentary where we follow a life journey of a young man, some parts of it recorded by his sister. Not an easy journey, but there is a place, a country which national anthem begins with the words from the film's title. We get many hints to answers of important questions of youth (and life). Should we follow dreams or conform with the life we are already living? For a start, check Arnaud's story.
